{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "edge-api-provisioning-001",
		"name": "rallymate Edge API - Provisioning Service",
		"description": "Bridge provisioning and lifecycle management. Handles bridge registration with the cloud backend, authentication token management, and unprovisioning.\n\n**Service**: edge.provisioning.ProvisioningService\n**Base URL**: http://{{bridge_ip}}:{{bridge_port}}\n**Port**: 8090 (default)\n**Authentication**: None (local bridge access)\n\n**Provisioning Flow**:\n1. User generates One-Time Code (OTC) in mobile app\n2. User enters OTC on bridge (via keypad/display)\n3. Bridge calls ProvisionWithOTC to register with cloud\n4. Bridge receives auth tokens and facility assignment\n5. Bridge operates with periodic token refresh\n6. Optional: ResetProvisioning to unprovision\n\n**Token Management**:\n- Initial tokens from ProvisionWithOTC\n- Periodic refresh via RefreshToken\n- Validation via ValidateToken\n- Status monitoring via GetProvisioningStatus",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
