						"description": "Provision bridge using a one-time code generated in the mobile app.\n\n**Endpoint**: POST /api/provision/otc\n**Request**: ProvisionWithOTCRequest\n**Response**: ProvisionResponse\n\n**Flow**:\n1. User generates OTC in mobile app (valid for 10 minutes)\n2. User enters OTC on bridge device\n3. Bridge sends OTC + device info to this endpoint\n4. Backend validates OTC and returns auth tokens + facility assignment\n5. Bridge stores tokens and begins operation\n\n**Request Fields**:\n- `one_time_code`: From mobile app (format: XXX-XXX-XXX)\n- `device_info`: Bridge metadata for registration\n\n**Response Fields**:\n- `success`: Provisioning succeeded\n- `access_token`: JWT for API authentication\n- `refresh_token`: Token for refreshing access\n- `facility_id`: Assigned facility\n- `backend_url`: Cloud API endpoint\n- `mqtt_config`: MQTT connection details"
